<bioghist altrender="biography" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
	<head>Biography</head>
	<p>Corporal <persname>Filias J. Plourd</persname> of <geogname>Hartford, CT</geogname>, served primarily in the post office of the 260th Infantry. A noncombatant over the age of thirty-five, his letters were sent primarily to his brother, Launce.</p>
<p></p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
	<head>Scope and Content</head>
	<p>The collection contains correspondence from Filias "Phil" to his brother, Launce.</p>
</scopecontent>
